<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>39</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zhè shì yé hé huá suǒ dìng de rì zi 迦南39</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhè shì yé hé huá suǒ dìng de rì zi, wǒ men yào zài qí zhōng gāo xìng huān xǐ;
 zhè shì yé hé huá suǒ dìng de rì zi, wǒ men yào zài qí zhōng gāo xìng huān xǐ;
 nǐ wǒ tā lái zì nán běi dōng xī, cóng yuǎn fāng xiāng jù dào zhè lǐ;
 mài bù tóng dēng yé hé huá de shān, lǐng shòu tā kǒu zhōng de yán yǔ.
 duō měi hǎo shén yǔ rén tóng jū, duō měi hǎo wǒ men yòu zài yī qǐ;
 chéng jià de de gāo chù, áng shǒu qīng tiān wài, xíng jìn zài zhǔ de cí ài lǐ.
 chǎng kāi nǐ de xīn líng, fàng shēng gāo chàng; shén de zhàng mù zài zhè lǐ!
 zhè shì yé hé huá suǒ dìng de rì zi, wǒ men yào zài qí zhōng gāo xìng huān xǐ.</lyrics>
</song>